      <h2>Migration cost to Plumego.</h2>
      <p>
        The decision to switch frameworks is rarely just about API ergonomics — it also involves handler
        rewrites, middleware replacements, and testing infrastructure. This table gives an honest estimate
        of the effort involved when migrating an existing service to Plumego.
